1.2 Scope\par
The application will manage the information about various students enrolled in this\par
course in different years, the subjects offered during different semesters of the course, the\par
marks obtained by the various students in various subjects in different semesters.\par
The application will greatly simplify and speed up the result preparation and management\par
process.\par
